&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this role, you would:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create videos and exercises for Khan Academy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously iterate and improve content based on feedback received.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
