&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internal Communication &amp;amp; Storytelling:&lt;/strong&gt; Effectively disseminate key learnings to the wider team. Translate synthesized data into engaging written communications (emails, newsletters), presentation decks, and active contributions during weekly team meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
